        Official Singles Chart on 29/1/2021

        29 January 2021 - 4 February 2021

        The Official UK Singles Chart reflects the UKs biggest songs of the week, based on audio and video streams, downloads, CDs and vinyl, compiled by the Official Charts Company. The UK Top 40 is broadcast on BBC Radio 1 and MTV, the Top 100 is published exclusively on OfficialCharts.com. View the biggest songs of 2024 so far.

        good afternoon all...

        i've been following this site for a few months, but never actually commented here, although since so many people are reviewing the charts right now, i thought i'd give it a go myself.

        hope you will enjoy. :)

        so, "drivers license" is still at number 1 with an insane lead. i really like the song personally, but i hope that overplayment on the radio doesn't ruin a really good song. that's what happened with "blinding lights" last year. :(

        "wellerman" being the highest new entry shows that really anything can happen in the charts in 2021! i didn't mind the original, but i think the remix by 220kid gives it far more life and energy, so it's good to see that version get credited here.

        i'm definiteiy rooting for "good days" to go top 10 soon too! sza has been making some incredible rnb for a while now, so it's so satisfying to see her finally get a solo hit in the uk. :)

        as for the other new entries, "back to basic" seemed okay on first listen but will have to grow on me, "skin" is very well-written but i don't like the drama between olivia and sabrina, "lo vas a olvidar" surprised me since i didn't know that billie eilish knew any spanish, just a shame that it bores me, sorry. :/

        "friday" has an addicting beat despite it being repetitive, "regardless" is very groovy and it sounds like a jax jones song more than a rudimental one... i prefer "be the one" though.

        finally, i'm very impressed to see glass animals get their first ever top 40 hit with "heat waves"! any reason why it's becoming so big now? did it go viral on tiktok or something? either way, it just makes want to have summer back right away, lol. ;)

        stay happy and healthy, friends. :)

        x
